00:42:04,063 --> 00:42:05,689
-Come on. Let's go.
-Let me go.

546
00:42:11,111 --> 00:42:12,655
Jae-min!

547
00:42:19,995 --> 00:42:20,996
Gosh.

548
00:42:21,622 --> 00:42:23,082
