-Really?

684
00:49:51,363 --> 00:49:52,572
-My gosh.
-Eat up.

685
00:49:52,656 --> 00:49:54,700
-What's going on over there?
-I see.

686
00:49:54,783 --> 00:49:56,868
-Who knows?
-My gosh, Dr. Cha.

687
00:49:56,952 --> 00:49:58,537
Don't you have lessons today?

688
00:49:59,621 --> 00:50:02,040
