00:51:18,450 --> 00:51:19,659
-See you!
-Bye, Seung-gi!

718
00:51:19,743 --> 00:51:20,786
-Get home safely.
-Bye!

719
00:51:20,869 --> 00:51:21,745
-Bye.
-Bye, Jae-min!

720
00:51:25,999 --> 00:51:27,834
All right, we're here.

721
00:51:31,546 --> 00:51:32,923
Thank you.

